text: Brainbombs is a compilation by Swedish noise rock band Brainbombs in 2007 by Polly Maggoo Records which compiles songs made by the band from 1993 to 2007. The last 12 tracks are from a show at ROCK ALL, Oslo. == Tracklist == == References == Category:Brainbombs albums Category:2007 albums
title: Brainbombs (2007 compilation)
